snippet.title: Knight Online World [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Knight Online is a leading party based medieval MMORPG that is, and will alyways be, Free to Play! Join the endless struggle of the Karus and El Morad nations as they wage war on eachother. This is the official facebook page for NTTGames Knight Online World. 

Join the greatest epic PvP War in Knight Online! http://portal.nttgame.com/
